          <article-title lang="foreign">A Study on Game Character Motion through analysis of Classic Game -Focusing on Historical Change of 2D Game Character Motion Sprite-</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">A Study on Game Character Motion through analysis of Classic Game -Focusing on Historical Change of 2D Game Character Motion Sprite-</article-title>
