          <article-title lang="original">모바일 소셜 게임 GUI 속성의 표현 분석 - 카카오톡과 페이스북 기반의 게임을 중심으로 -</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">A study of mobile social game's GUI elementary expression - Focused on Kakaotalk games and Facebook games</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">A study of mobile social game's GUI elementary expression - Focused on Kakaotalk games and Facebook games</article-title>
