          <article-title lang="foreign">A Comparison Analysis of Game Interface usability for PC Game and Apply Touch Screen Mobile Game - Focusing on FIFA Soccer 14 -</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">A Comparison Analysis of Game Interface usability for PC Game and Apply Touch Screen Mobile Game - Focusing on FIFA Soccer 14 -</article-title>
