          <article-title lang="original">게임 엔진의 기술 체제에 따른 게임 개발 성과 차이에 관한 연구</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">A Impact of Technological Regime of Game Engine upon Game Development Performance</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">A Impact of Technological Regime of Game Engine upon Game Development Performance</article-title>
