        <title-group>
          <article-title lang="original">게임 플랫폼과 게임 이용 형태의 변화에 따른 포스트 코로나 시대의 게임산업 경쟁력 방안 연구</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Study on the Competitiveness Plan of the Game Industry in the Post Corona Era according to Changes of Game Platforms and Game Use Types</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Study on the Competitiveness Plan of the Game Industry in the Post Corona Era according to Changes of Game Platforms and Game Use Types</article-title>
        </title-group>
