          <article-title lang="original">제인 오스틴과 게임하기--『에마』에 나타난 게임 모티브와 독자</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Playing Games with Jane Austen: The Game Motif and the Reader in Emma</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Playing Games with Jane Austen: The Game Motif and the Reader in Emma</article-title>
        </title-group>
