          <article-title lang="foreign">Two-Face Game : An Alternative to Robert D. Putnam's Two-Level Game Theory</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Two-Face Game : An Alternative to Robert D. Putnam's Two-Level Game Theory</article-title>
