          <article-title lang="original">게임 과몰입과 중독에 영향을 미치는 게임 요소와 메커니즘 연구</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Research on the Game Elements and Mechanism that Affect the Game Overindulgence and Addiction</article-title>
