        <title-group>
          <article-title lang="original">게임 캐릭터가 플레이 의향에 미치는 영향 - 롤플레잉 게임(RPG)에서 관능적 캐릭터 호감도를 중심으로</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">The Effects of Game Character Design on the Game Playing Intention: Focused On Sexual Female Character Design in Role-Playing Games</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">The Effects of Game Character Design on the Game Playing Intention: Focused On Sexual Female Character Design in Role-Playing Games</article-title>
