          <article-title lang="original">1인 게임방송의 긍정적 효과성에 관한 연구: 게임 효능감을 중심으로</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">A Study on Positive Effects of Personal Game Broadcasting: Focusing on Game Efficacy</article-title>
