          <article-title lang="original">중국 웹보드 게임 정책 분석: '비엔펑' 게임사례를 중심으로</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">The Analysis for Web-board Game Policy in China : The Case Study for 'Bianfeng' Game</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">The Analysis for Web-board Game Policy in China : The Case Study for 'Bianfeng' Game</article-title>
