          <article-title lang="original">온라인게임 운영 서비스와 콘텐츠 만족도가 게임 충성도에 미치는 영향에 대한 연구</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">Effects of Online Game Service Satisfaction and Content Satisfaction on Users' Game Loyalty</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">Effects of Online Game Service Satisfaction and Content Satisfaction on Users' Game Loyalty</article-title>
