          <article-title lang="original">온라인 게임갈망에 대한 대처방략이 청소년의 게임중독에 미치는 영향</article-title>
          <article-title lang="foreign">The Effects of the Coping Strategies of Online Game Craving on Adolescents' Game Addiction</article-title>
          <article-title lang="english">The Effects of the Coping Strategies of Online Game Craving on Adolescents' Game Addiction</article-title>
        </title-group>
        <author-group>
